Ruby/Libgda
==============

Ruby/Libgda is a Ruby binding of libgda (GNOME-DB Project). 

Requirements
------------

    Ruby:           http://www.ruby-lang.org/
    libgda [*]:     http://www.gnome-db.org/

    [*]: 1.1.99 or newer is required.

Install
-------

    0. install ruby and libgda. 
    1. ruby extconf.rb
    2. make
    3. su
    4. make install

